---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Accessibility Statement - The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-8) 0; max-width: 800px;">
    
    <header class="reveal-on-scroll" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); text-align:center;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Accessibility Statement</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-1" style="border: none; box-shadow: none; background-color: var(--color-bg); padding: 0;">
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
        The WEL Foundation is firmly committed to ensuring digital and physical accessibility for all individuals, including those with disabilities. We continually improve the user experience for everyone, and we adhere strictly to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA standards to provide robust digital equity.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue); margin-top: var(--spacing-6); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Measures to Support Accessibility</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">The WEL Foundation takes the following rigorous measures to ensure the accessibility of our services:</p>
      <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
        <li>Integrating accessibility deeply into our physical clinical infrastructure alongside our digital platforms.</li>
        <li>Providing continuous accessibility training for our staff and clinical teams.</li>
        <li>Assigning clear accessibility targets and tracking clinical and communicative outcomes.</li>
        <li>Employing strict color contrast thresholds, semantic HTML, and screen-reader compliant structural layouts on our web platform.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue); margin-top: var(--spacing-6); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Feedback & Accommodation Requests</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">
        If you require special accommodations during an intake evaluation, or if you encounter accessibility barriers while navigating our digital experiences, we want to hear from you immediately. We try to respond to feedback within 48 business hours.
      </p>
      
      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); padding: var(--spacing-4); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-top: var(--spacing-4);">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
          <strong>Phone:</strong> 443-826-2770<br/>
          <strong>Email:</strong> accessibility@weempowerleadership.com<br/>
          <strong>Postal Address:</strong> 5858 Belair Rd, Baltimore, MD 21206
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
